何對峙都係差佬佔9成上風, 問題係佢幾時攻你!<br />\n大量義士被捕、受傷 !<br />\n狗屋已經有差佬開槍暗殺 ! <br />\n浪費體力破壞死物, 差佬有損失嗎? 會驚到唔敢返工嗎 ? <br />\n8萬一個月撚死你班暴徒, 多謝黎唔切 !<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對準有效行動</span></strong></span><br />\n1) 全面佔領機場<br />\n普通市民受阻礙最低, 效果最高 !<br />\n從來國際新聞都只報機場被佔領 !<br />\n機場被佔領, 代表遊客是零 !<br />\n<br />\n2) 遊擊攻打差佬<br />\n現在唯一障礙, 一定要攻破 !<br />\n唔好再廢up差佬就黎爆煲, 8萬一個月唔夠可以再加 !<br />\n差佬心底話:你地咁樣唔會令到我驚架 !<br />\n因為返工根本無生命危險! <br />\n再講依家係軍政府管治, 請你當佢地軍人看待 !<br />\n軍人上戰場預左會死 ! <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n附上影片 : <br />\n警例亦已無效 , 軍人撚到市民傻 hihi ! <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/561356720/posts/10156152865921721?s=1529187886&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F561356720%2Fposts%2F10156152865921721%3Fs%3D1529187886%26sfns%3Dmo&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWC%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=88634cac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/561356720/posts/10156152865921721?s=1529187886&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/295202647488775/permalink/1753276658348026?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F295202647488775%2Fpermalink%2F1753276658348026%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWC%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=623b7e3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/295202647488775/permalink/1753276658348026?sfns=mo</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:40:59.000Z","msg":"我幫你再講白少少<br />\n令到狗狗有生命危險<br />\n特別休息果時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申講緊gta"},{"pid":"dc7b8c688c0611d2c04b0d4299cf84f0c488cb83","tid":1412654,"uid":156767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab4529c1186d40d3ba47c33019c6cee33f7833e","tid":1412654,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT